txt.en: Bog-lurkers have been creeping into Makham Mijann.
It seems that once dismantling efforts in Makham Mijann ground to a halt, bog-lurkers began creeping in.\n\nYou should clear some out of the area to make their numbers more manageable.
You have defeated many bog-lurkers at Makham Mijann. When the residents of Tadrent return to dismantle the rest of the camp, they should have no problem with the bog-lurkers.
Makham Mijann has been overrun by bog-lurkers!
You have defeated many bog-lurkers at Makham Mijann.
You should clear some bog-lurkers out of Makham Mijann to make their numbers more manageable.\n\nMakham Mijann is located to the north of Tadrent.
